data.description: ***  NEW PRICE and seller to pay $2500.00 in purchasers closing costs with an acceptable offer ***   Daylight pours into this cozy home!  2 bedrooms and 1 full bath, detached garage and driveway with ample parking.  Also featuring original hardwood floors, laundry space and bonus room.  This spacious flat yard has incredible entertaining and gardening ability.  A short walk from Patriot Park and Hall-Kent Elementary. 2017 roof replacement on house and garage. Take a look today.
